game.name: Frozen Family Dress Up
game.description:
The biggest funny and challenging brand new dressing game has been launched today and you should immediately join it to polish your sharp fashion abilities. In Frozen Family Dress Up game, you would meet with the two lovely couples Anna and Kristoff and Elsa and Jack who want to dress themselves in different styles. Will you come forward to dress them up all? Join this unique fun challenge and help them get ready in different four styles! Hurry up, ladies! Two girls are waiting for their new party looks. 
Choose any style from different four options including Fashion, Home Clothes, Sports and Royal ball in this brand new dressing game for girls! Start with a right kind of hairstyle and combine it with a t-shirt and jeans or long top and legging or an elegant legging in Fashion style! Give your chosen girl a pair of matching sandals, earrings, necklace and a nice guitar! In Home Clothes style, you can make the changes in her hairstyle, and give her a nice night suit or a comfortable t-shirt and short nicker. 
The Sports style also allows you to play with different hairstyles, sports dresses, shoes, jewelries and sports bag. Practice your fashion abilities for the both princesses in this html5 dress up game! You would get a chance to explore multiple designer gowns in the final and fourth Royal Ball style. Give her a nice hairstyle and make her shine with a pair of elegant shoes, earrings and necklace and a matching handbag!
